<item>
            <title>[LU-11083] uninstalled llmount.sh fails due to dependency on crc_t10dif()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11083</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;obdclass.ko now depends on &lt;tt&gt;crc_t10dif()&lt;/tt&gt; which is provided by the &lt;tt&gt;crc_t10dif&lt;/tt&gt; kernel module. In lustre/tests/test-framework.sh &lt;tt&gt;load_modules_local()&lt;/tt&gt; we should handle this in a similar way to the dependencies on crc and jbd2.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
